_sText:
Fy_cityworld_css - Team Deathmatch
Version 1.0
Map by David Alner AKA !=supa-sexy-n00b=!
Compiled with Source SDK

History:
--------
1.0 (Beta 1) - 	First port from original CS version (HL1 Engine).
    (Beta 2) -  Added more obstacles for more compact gameplay.

Known Issues:
-------------
- No weapons at spawn, only buyzones. Will be replaced with weapons once SDK is updated to support addition of weapon ammo.

Description:
------------
This is a FY map. Buyzones are at each of the spawns. This level takes place in a small city block. Terrorists and Counter-Terrorists start on opposite sides of the map. Secret room somewhere in the map. Enjoy! =)

Objectives:
-----------
Both teams: Eliminate the enemy force.



Credits:
--------
 MadBimber - Original map idea.
